// NOTE: A previous harvested rule rewrote any `.toString()` call on an
// IPath into `.toOSString()`. That changes semantics (path separator,
// trailing '/' handling) and matched all `.toString()` calls before any
// guard could filter — removed.

new org.eclipse.core.runtime.SubProgressMonitor($monitor, $amount)
=> org.eclipse.core.runtime.SubMonitor.convert($monitor, $amount)
;;

