@id: eclipse.jdt.core.javacore.runreadonly.removewrapper
@severity: info
"Removes the JavaCore.runReadOnly() wrapper around expressions in lambdas, addressing regressions where UI operations could conflict with read-only blocks. This partial revert improves runtime stability.":
org.eclipse.jdt.core.JavaCore.runReadOnly(() -> $expression$)
=> $expression$
;;

@id: eclipse.jdt.core.javacore.callreadonly.removewrapper
