"Removes the JavaCore.callReadOnly() wrapper around expressions in lambdas, addressing regressions where UI operations could conflict with read-only blocks. This partial revert improves runtime stability.":
org.eclipse.jdt.core.JavaCore.callReadOnly(() -> $expression$)
=> $expression$
;;

